    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="影单"><a href="#影单" class="headerlink" title="影单"></a>影单</h2><table><thead><tr><th>Date</th><th></th><th>Rating</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>9th</td><td><a href="#Flow-2024"><em>Flow (2024)</em></a></td><td>5🌟</td></tr><tr><td>10th</td><td><a href="#Every-Little-Thing-2024"><em>Every Little Thing (2024)</em></a></td><td>3.5🌟</td></tr><tr><td>12th</td><td><a href="#%E7%A0%B4%E7%A2%8E%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E4%B9%8B%E5%BF%83-2022"><em>破碎太阳之心 (2022)</em></a></td><td>3🌟</td></tr><tr><td>16th</td><td><a href="#Black-Bag-2025"><em>Black Bag (2025)</em></a></td><td>2🌟</td></tr><tr><td>19th</td><td><a href="#%E6%9A%91%E5%81%87-2020"><em>暑假 (2020)</em></a></td><td>5🌟</td></tr><tr><td>27th</td><td><a href="#%E8%8A%B1%E6%A0%B7%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%8E-2000"><em>花样年华 (2000) 25周年重映</em></a></td><td>4🌟</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="书单"><a href="#书单" class="headerlink" title="书单"></a>书单</h2><table><thead><tr><th></th><th>Rating</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href="#%E5%A4%8F%E6%97%A5%E8%B0%8E%E8%A8%80"><em>夏日谎言</em></a></td><td>5🌟</td></tr><tr><td><a href="#%E9%85%92%E5%BE%92"><em>酒徒</em></a></td><td>3.5🌟</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="歌单"><a href="#歌单" class="headerlink" title="歌单"></a>歌单</h2><p>moon tang - ‘25’</p><blockquote><p>好听: for you | 夜闌人靜 </p></blockquote><h2 id="影评"><a href="#影评" class="headerlink" title="影评"></a>影评</h2><h3 id="Flow-2024"><a href="#Flow-2024" class="headerlink" title="Flow (2024)"></a>Flow (2024)</h3><p>一部淡淡的动画～<br>P.S. 在悉尼看的点映，彼时布里斯班正在发洪水。</p><h3 id="Every-Little-Thing-2024"><a href="#Every-Little-Thing-2024" class="headerlink" title="Every Little Thing (2024)"></a>Every Little Thing (2024)</h3><p>节奏太拖沓。商业味太重，看完没什么印象。</p><h3 id="破碎太阳之心-2022"><a href="#破碎太阳之心-2022" class="headerlink" title="破碎太阳之心 (2022)"></a>破碎太阳之心 (2022)</h3><p>拼好片。</p><h3 id="Black-Bag-2025"><a href="#Black-Bag-2025" class="headerlink" title="Black Bag (2025)"></a>Black Bag (2025)</h3><p>真人版“间谍过家家”。没有什么大场面，可以安心睡觉。</p><h3 id="暑假-2020"><a href="#暑假-2020" class="headerlink" title="暑假 (2020)"></a>暑假 (2020)</h3><p>近期最爱的下饭综艺。我也好想过暑假呀～</p><h3 id="花样年华-2000"><a href="#花样年华-2000" class="headerlink" title="花样年华 (2000)"></a>花样年华 (2000)</h3><blockquote><p>是我，如果有多一张船票，你会不会跟我一起走？</p></blockquote><p>情不知所起，一往而深，如梦。<br>爱未及成诗，倏然而逝，如烟。<br>期间青葱岁月，名曰花样年华。</p><h2 id="书评"><a href="#书评" class="headerlink" title="书评"></a>书评</h2><h3 id="夏日谎言"><a href="#夏日谎言" class="headerlink" title="夏日谎言"></a>夏日谎言</h3><p>七篇好读的情感短篇。</p><h3 id="酒徒"><a href="#酒徒" class="headerlink" title="酒徒"></a>酒徒</h3><p>一本文字顺畅但难读的书。文笔惊艳。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
